 1→// lib/serval-tls/stream.zig
 2→//! TLS stream abstraction
 3→//!
 4→//! Provides unified interface for TLS I/O operations with two modes:
 5→//! - Userspace mode: TLS via BoringSSL SSL object (default after handshake)
 6→//! - kTLS mode: Kernel TLS offload for symmetric crypto (upgrade from userspace)
 7→//!
 8→//! This module uses blocking SSL operations. The underlying socket is managed
