Replace:
```zig
fn resolveServerAlpnMixedOfferPolicy(arg: ?*anyopaque) AlpnMixedOfferPolicy {
    if (arg) |raw| {
        const policy_ptr: *const AlpnMixedOfferPolicy = @ptrCast(@alignCast(raw));
