```

**Step 6: Handle gracefully in deinit (log and return, don't crash)**

Replace:
```zig
    pub fn deinit(self: *ReloadableServerCtx) void {
        assert(@intFromPtr(self) != 0);

        lockMutex(&self.mutex);
        defer self.mutex.unlock();
```

With:
```zig
    pub fn deinit(self: *ReloadableServerCtx) void {
        assert(@intFromPtr(self) != 0);

